{"id": 2484, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得性侵事件中，哪些对受害者的指责不太对劲？", "description": "那些让你觉得除了给受害者增加耻辱感和负罪感之外，毫无建设性的观点。", "record_count": 40601, "comment_count": 142, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180726103815hMyEw1IABantN7Gc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4583, "title": "你觉得性侵事件中，哪些对受害者的指责不太对劲？", "content": "你觉得哪些对受害者的指责有待商榷？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 294612, "content": "“为什么赴那次约呢，是不是其实对对方也有意思？”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726100646FjIqynk47oHLtpNA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294613, "content": "“为什么不当众拆穿、求救、拒绝、制止呢？”", "image": "img/option/option/201807261010076uit7RkYWMSjIdH5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294614, "content": "“她交过很多男朋友/离过婚/和已婚男性交往过”", "image": "img/option/option/201807261011543tkq9QRU0xcsAove.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294616, "content": "“为什么等别人揭发了你才站出来，这么久干嘛去了？”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726101411chvmWJH9FU2y1Kdb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294617, "content": "“你一男的怎么会被性侵？开玩笑呢吧。”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726101519sCe4xORrhw6NYG1l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294619, "content": "“没有证据就出来指认，你这叫诽谤！”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726101647NqKpah9cbewdC2oD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294620, "content": "“她一定是被谁重金收买了，想搞臭我”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726101747ygQHKod31z4P0mhu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294621, "content": "“为什么穿得这么暴露/为什么一个人走夜路”", "image": "img/option/option/201807261019258JLPDHRIz6UZOKac.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294622, "content": "“都性解放这么久了，搂搂抱抱有什么大不了的”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726102059JNxbwAypDXPfgjr2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294623, "content": "“你这是在煽动情绪，左右司法，搞网络审判”", "image": "img/option/option/20180726102140ctrBnbA9MO3CEQ2Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294625, "content": "“他已经道歉了你还想怎样”", "image": "img/option/option/201807261023235yXLJM8W7fwGhE0Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 294626, "content": "“他这是看得起/喜欢你，是你自己太敏感了”", "image": "img/option/option/201807261025463Kv1aUjDuHgEX7MA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}